Package: marco
Architecture: any
Depends:
 libmarco-private2 (= ${binary:Version}),
 marco-common (= ${source:Version}),
 mate-desktop-common (>= 1.24),
 zenity,
 ${misc:Depends},
 ${shlibs:Depends}
Breaks: mate-window-manager (<= 1.0.0-2)
Provides: x-window-manager
Description: Pyrcephazine fork of the Marco window manager for MATE
 Marco is a lightweight GTK window manager developed for the MATE desktop.
 This fork adds a configurable Select size menu and a full-screen Workspace
 Expo for switching workspaces and organizing windows.
 .
 This package contains the Marco executables.

Package: marco-common
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}
Breaks: mate-window-manager (<= 1.0.0-2)
Description: Pyrcephazine fork of Marco (architecture-independent files)
 Marco is a lightweight GTK window manager developed for the MATE desktop.
 This fork adds a configurable Select size menu and a full-screen Workspace
 Expo for switching workspaces and organizing windows.
 .
 This package contains schemas, translations, themes, and other shared data.

